title: My 15 Books - June 2014 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 15 books for this month all in ePUB format this time with covers included in a separate folder:

01. 1177 B.C. - The Year Civilization Collapsed
02. All Over the Map - Writing on Buildings and Cities
03. Buffi's Dress Design - Sew 30 Fun Styles Make It, Own It, Rock It
04. Eat What You Love--Everyday! - 200 All-New, Great-Tasting Recipes Low in Sugar, Fat, and Calories
05. Five Point Touch Therapy - Acupressure for the Emotional Body
06. Josey Baker Bread - Get Baking - Make Awesome Bread - Share the Loaves
07. Modern Construction Management (7th Ed)
08. Popular Music and the New Auteur - Visionary Filmmakers after MTV
09. Posing for Portrait and Glamour Photography - Techniques for Digital Photographers
10. Stitch 'n Swap - 25 Handmade Projects to Sew, Give & Receive
11. Sun Sign Secrets - The Complete Astrology Guide to Love, Work, and Your Future
12. The Handy Chemistry Answer Book
13. The Hiltons - The True Story of an American Dynasty
14. The Rooftop Beekeeper - A Scrappy Guide to Keeping Urban Honeybees
15. Among Wolves - Gordon Haber's Insights into Alaska's Most Misunderstood Animal
